      • matchOntClass

        public com.hp.hpl.jena.ontology.OntClass matchOntClass(com.hp.hpl.jena.ontology.OntModel ontModel,
                                              CharSequence path)
        Given a relative URI, returns ontology class with a matching URI template, if any. By default, lda:uriTemplate property (from Linked Data API) is used for the owl:HasValue restrictions, with URI template string as the object literal.
        Parameters:
        ontModel - sitemap ontology model
        path - absolute path (relative URI)
        Returns:
        matching ontology class or null, if none
        See Also:
        Linked Data API Vocabulary

      • matchOntClass

        public com.hp.hpl.jena.ontology.OntClass matchOntClass(com.hp.hpl.jena.ontology.OntModel ontModel,
                                              CharSequence path,
                                              com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.Property property)
        Given a relative URI and URI template property, returns ontology class with a matching URI template, if any. URIs are matched against the URI templates specified in resource templates (sitemap ontology classes). Templates in the base ontology model have priority (are matched first) against templates in imported ontologies.
        Parameters:
        ontModel - sitemap ontology model
        path - absolute path (relative URI)
        property - restriction property holding the URI template value
        Returns:
        matching ontology class or null, if none
        See Also:
        3.7 Matching Requests to Resource Methods (JAX-RS 1.1), Jersey UriTemplate, Jena HasValueRestriction

      • matchOntClasses

        Matches path (relative URI) against URI templates in sitemap ontology. This method uses Jersey implementation of the JAX-RS URI matching algorithm.
        Parameters:
        ontModel - sitemap ontology model
        path - URI path
        property - property attaching URI templates to ontology class
        inBaseModel - whether to only use base model statements

        URI template/ontology class map
